headline: Aude Gandon Appointed Chief Digital & Marketing Officer, The Estée Lauder Companies
summary: NEW YORK, July 16, 2025--The Estée Lauder Companies Inc. (NYSE: EL) announced today that Aude Gandon has been appointed Chief Digital & Marketing Officer (CDMO), effective August 1, 2025. Ms. Gandon will report directly to Stéphane de La Faverie, President and Chief Executive Officer, and will join the company's Executive Team.
